      • addNode

        public int addNode(node_type node)
        Given a node this method first checks to see if the node has been added previously but is now innactive. If it is, it is reactivated. If the node has not been added previously, it is checked to make sure its index matches the next node index before being added to the graph

      • addEdge

        public void addEdge(edge_type edge)
        Use this to add an edge to the graph. The method will ensure that the edge passed as a parameter is valid before adding it to the graph. If the graph is a digraph then a similar edge connecting the nodes in the opposite direction will be automatically added.
